# Generator test that consumes a packing.dat file produced (or hand-written
# in the same format) by aggregate. Each `sphere` line becomes an
# InterfaceSphere with the directive's itz/refine.
#@output nodes.dat
#@domain 3
#@diam 4.e-3
#@maxiter 1000
#@ranint -1
#@perflag 3 1 1 1
#@ranflag 2
# bounding-box corners widen the localiser for periodic neighbour lookup
#@vertex 1 coords 3 -0.025 -0.025 -0.025
#@vertex 2 coords 3  0.075  0.075  0.075
#@prism 1 box 6 0. 0. 0. 0.05 0.05 0.05 refine 1.
#@inclusionfile packing.dat itz 0.5e-3 refine 0.5
